How about this though - a spell which adds clones of your current pet, that take the damage for your pet.  Basically it would be a graphical pet rune similar to Calliav.  Cast it, you suddenly have 4 pets beating on the mob (only one of which is actually doing DPS).  Mob takes a few swings at your pet, when it hits 1000 hp or whatever fair value is, one pet image poofs, without leaving damage on the real pet.
